<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٤٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6106">مُسْلِمٌ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1580">الْحَكَمِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1904">ذَرٍّ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2395">ابْنِ عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3214">عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ </a>قَالَ: شَهِدْتُ عُمَرَ فَقَالَ لَهُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4621">عَمَّارٌ </a>: وَسَاقَ الْحَدِيثَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>